{"id":543058,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/10/【立此存照】论爱国的常识：纪念红军还是纪/","date":"2016-10-22T04:01:30Z","modified":"2016-10-22T04:01:30Z","title":"【立此存照】论“爱国”的常识：纪念红军还是纪念红卫兵","content":"<p>【编者注】为配合中共官方纪念长征胜利的活动，新浪微博近日推出了一套“长征特别版小红军卡通贴纸”。该系列贴纸曾错误地使用了65式军服的绿色作为红军军服颜色，这使得所谓的“小红军”形象看起来更像是“<strong>小红卫兵</strong>”。在10月21日正式上线前的推广期间，经网民指出错误后，新浪微博对此进行了修改，并删除了最早推广绿色红军军服的微博。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/小红军贴纸1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-543059\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/小红军贴纸1.jpg\" alt=\"小红军贴纸1\" width=\"500\" height=\"466\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/小红军贴纸1.jpg 1208w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/小红军贴纸1-300x280.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/小红军贴纸1-768x716.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/小红军贴纸1-1024x954.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/小红军贴纸2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-543060\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/小红军贴纸2.jpg\" alt=\"小红军贴纸2\" width=\"350\" height=\"467\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/小红军贴纸2.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/小红军贴纸2-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>@战争史研究WHS：我怎么记得红军的军服应该是深灰色（染料便宜、土布染色方便）？这个军绿色的应该是65式军服吧？</strong></p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/红军服装.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-543062\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/红军服装.jpg\" alt=\"红军服装\" width=\"440\" height=\"612\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/红军服装.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/红军服装-216x300.jpg 216w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/小红军贴纸4.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-543063\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/小红军贴纸4.jpg\" alt=\"小红军贴纸4\" width=\"500\" height=\"388\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/小红军贴纸4.jpg 1200w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/小红军贴纸4-300x233.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/小红军贴纸4-768x596.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/小红军贴纸4-1024x795.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/7a5f39b3jw1f8z5ta8kd8j20go0m8ju5.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-543065\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/7a5f39b3jw1f8z5ta8kd8j20go0m8ju5.jpg\" alt=\"7a5f39b3jw1f8z5ta8kd8j20go0m8ju5\" width=\"350\" height=\"467\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/7a5f39b3jw1f8z5ta8kd8j20go0m8ju5.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/7a5f39b3jw1f8z5ta8kd8j20go0m8ju5-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[18804,20440,23589,30038,8859,21038,21268]}